properties.Name: ScheduledLearningEvent
properties.Description: A LEARNING EVENT performed at a specific location upon a scheduled date/time.

Columns.Name: ScheduledLearningEventId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Scheduled Learning Event.

Columns.Name: LearningEventId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Learning Event.

Columns.Name: LearningEventScheduledStartDate
Columns.Description: The scheduled start date for the Learning Event at the associated Training Site Location.

Columns.Name: LearningEventScheduledStartTime
Columns.Description: The scheduled first day start time for the Learning Event at the associated Training Site Location.

Columns.Name: LearningEventScheduledEndDate
Columns.Description: The scheduled end date for the Learning Event at the associated Training Site Location.

Columns.Name: LearningEventScheduledEndTime
Columns.Description: The scheduled last day ending time for the Learning Event at the associated Training Site Location.

Columns.Name: LearningEventStartDate
Columns.Description: The start date for the Learning Event at the associated Training Site Location.

Columns.Name: LearningEventStartTime
Columns.Description: The start time for the Learning Event at the associated Training Site Location.

Columns.Name: LearningEventEndDate
Columns.Description: The end date for the Learning Event at the associated Training Site Location.

Columns.Name: LearningEventEndTime
Columns.Description: The ending time for the Learning Event at the associated Training Site Location.

Columns.Name: PlannedNumberAttendees
Columns.Description: The planned for number of attendees for the Scheduled Learning Event.

Columns.Name: ActualNumberAttendees
Columns.Description: The actual for number of attendees for the Scheduled Learning Event.

Columns.Name: PlannedNumberOfInstructionHours
Columns.Description: The planned number of instruction hours to be assigned to complete the Scheduled Learning Event.

Columns.Name: ConfirmationByDate
Columns.Description: The date by which confirmation must be received in order to be considered for the scheduled learning event.

Columns.Name: DepositMustBeReceivedByDate
Columns.Description: The date by which the deposit must be received in order to hold the position in the scheduled learning event.

Columns.Name: TotalCostToProduceLearningEvent
Columns.Description: The total cost to produce the Scheduled Learning Event at the associated Learning Site Location.

Columns.Name: TotalRevenueFromLearningEvent
Columns.Description: The total revenues generated by presentation of the Scheduled Learning Event.

Columns.Name: DeliveryChannelId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Delivery Channel.

Columns.Name: TvLearningEventId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of an TV Learning Event.

Columns.Name: RadioLearningEventId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of an Advertising Event.

Columns.Name: InternetLearningEventUrl
Columns.Description: The web page (URL) associated with the Internet Learning Event.

Columns.Name: LearningEventStatusTypeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of the Learning Event Status Type.

Columns.Name: LocationId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Location.

Columns.Name: VenueTypeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Venue Type.

Columns.Name: PublicationId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Publication.

Columns.Name: IsoLanguageId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of an ISO Language.

Columns.Name: ItemSku
Columns.Description: The Stock Keeping Unit identifier, which is typically used for inventory-related activities.
